#### Status Codes
Code | Name | Description
----- | ----------------------- | -----------------------------------
40601 | FEATURE_NOT_ENABLED | Messaging feature is not enabled for app.
40001 | APP_ERROR | Not supported for sharded message boxes. Use SysGetMessagesForOwnerPage API instead.

